title: Shadowrun Collection
description:
This is a huge collection with Shadowrun books.
It contains:
- All the 1st edition books
- All the 2nd edition books
- All the 3rd edition books
- Almost all the 4th edition books
- Almost all the released 5th edition books

It's separated in:
- Rluebooks
- Sourcebooks
- Missions/Adventures
- Novels
- Magazines
- Misc. content

The missing books/material is listed on the html file in the root folder.
Last update: 27-March-2014
